spanGrp.span: Teo peho vuri teitei roho a bua sii tom maagee.
Once upon a time there were two friends.
A bua sii tom maagee bari ere Horivana bo Moogee.
These two friends were Hurricane and Monkey.
Merau meori paa paku roho bono vamokomoko teori.
And so (one day), they had a competition.
E Moogee kou na sue roho,
"Sii otei ean sa antee haa tea vaakuu anaa teo naono!"
"Dear man, you cannot make me fall down from the tree!",
Me Horivana paa sue ki bona, "Sii otei, enaa na antee rakaha nom tea vaakuu vuan."
And Hurricane said to him, "Dear man, I can indeed make you fall down."
Merau meori paa nao teo peho vuri meori -
